short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Recommends Google Meet performance settings based on device CPU/memory.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Meet SPECulator helps determine the recommended settings for Google Meet based on your device's CPU and RAM. These settings include tiled or spotlight layout, presenting, high definition 720p video and max other tabs / apps the user should have running.
